{"tid":2396131,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黎智英保釋終審案 下周二將頒下判詞","createTime":"2021-02-05T10:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T22:00:53.000Z","uid":292499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d78cf45fee9b361ee7831d9cc61352b4ec597e17","tid":2396131,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"司法機構網頁顯示，終審法院將於下周二頒佈判詞。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n若終院裁定律政司上訴得直，即法官李運騰犯錯，便會撤銷批准保釋的決定，黎智英要再向高院或其他適當法院重新申請保釋。若終院駁回上訴，黎則獲釋，保釋繼續有效。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/HJDYYJQ7UZANHKBJ5T537UEKYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FHJDYYJQ7UZANHKBJ5T537UEKYQ%2F&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjNqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=471ce004\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FHJDYYJQ7UZANHKBJ5T537UEKYQ%2F&h=2a088f2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/HJDYYJQ7UZANHKBJ5T537UEKYQ/</a>"},{"pid":"fdb171f182f2815754a40e0c26218632489442da","tid":2396131,"uid":221395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:45:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba8f17d45a9d0fc13f357e4951a0aea93af7d7b","tid":2396131,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10:45:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b71428d92ac7de90ea72fcfc11f6eed28ce3476","tid":2396131,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdb